@startuml Sequence Diagram - Expense Tracker

skinparam sequenceArrowColor #5B2D8E
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #5B2D8E
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #5B2D8E
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #F0EBF8
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #999999
skinparam title {
    FontSize 18
    FontStyle Bold
}

title Sequence Diagram – Expense Tracker Application

actor User
participant "LoginScreen" as LS
participant "SignupScreen" as SS
participant "HomeScreen" as HS
participant "AddExpenseScreen" as AES
participant "FirebaseAuth" as FA
participant "FirebaseFirestore" as FF

== User Registration ==
User -> SS : Open Sign Up screen
SS -> FA : createUserWithEmailAndPassword(email, password)
FA --> SS : UserCredential (success)
SS -> FF : save user profile (username, email)
FF --> SS : confirmation
SS --> User : Navigate to Login screen

== User Login ==
User -> LS : Enter email & password
LS -> FA : signInWithEmailAndPassword(email, password)
FA --> LS : UserCredential (success)
LS --> User : Navigate to HomeScreen

== View Expenses ==
User -> HS : Open HomeScreen
HS -> FF : getExpensesStream() (real-time listener)
FF --> HS : Stream<QuerySnapshot>
HS --> User : Display expense list + total

== Add Expense ==
User -> HS : Tap "+" button
HS --> User : Navigate to AddExpenseScreen
User -> AES : Enter title, amount, category
AES -> FF : add({title, amount, category, date, timestamp})
FF --> AES : DocumentReference (success)
AES --> User : Navigate back to HomeScreen
HS -> FF : Stream updated automatically
FF --> HS : Updated expense list
HS --> User : Display updated total & list

== Delete Expense ==
User -> HS : Long-press to select expense(s)
HS --> User : Show selection mode UI
User -> HS : Tap delete icon
HS --> User : Confirm deletion dialog
User -> HS : Confirm
HS -> FF : delete(docId)
FF --> HS : Confirmation
HS --> User : Updated expense list

== Logout ==
User -> HS : Tap logout icon
HS -> FA : signOut()
FA --> HS : Success
HS --> User : Navigate to LoginScreen

@enduml
